{
  "stem": "4226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 206,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were also high school students, mainly the same age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 207,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there were quite a few-- lots of fights.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 208,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That happened, too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 208,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It happened--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 209,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because they-- someone beat his friend up a few days earlier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 209,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he, he just knew who he was, and he was just talking to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 210,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 211,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 211,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they also-- see, in the middle of the Second World War, our school was requisitioned by the government and made into a military hospital, with wounded Hungarian soldiers from the front.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 212,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were put into a girls' school for afternoon shift.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 212,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they finished 1 o'clock or 2:00.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 212,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started from 2:00 till 7:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 212,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was quite fun because you could leave notes-- [LAUGHTER] --and meet the girl who was sitting in the same bench in the morning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 212,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 213,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we met some girls like that, that way, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 213,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that went on for how long?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 214,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, that went on till, till we were deported.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 214,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we never got our school building back--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 215,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because the war was still going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 215,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- they were-- they're having more and more wounded people from the front line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 216,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 216,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1940, it became Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 217,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 217,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It became Hungary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 218,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 219,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Part of, of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 220,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the, when the war broke out with the Soviet Union, then--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 221,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember, actually, the days when German troops moved down through our township by train and, and mechanized units to-- before they attacked Greece and Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 221,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They built up their forces close to the-- those borders.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 221,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went through Hungary and Romania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 222,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 222,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of them stopped for two, three hours in, in the station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 222,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of these German soldiers came out and bought goods.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
